flowchart TD
    Start(["User message"]) --> Boot{"First trigger<br/>this conversation?"}
    Boot -->|yes| BootSteps["Step 0.5 Self-Bootstrap<br/>・Global rules reinforced?<br/>・knowledge-base empty?→suggest seed.py"]
    Boot -->|no| Extract
    BootSteps --> Extract

    Extract["Step 1　Extract Keywords<br/>3-8 core terms; first 3 become topic_fingerprint"] --> TopicSwitch{"Step 2　Topic Switch?<br/>transition words／keyword diff≥40%／new-category request"}

    TopicSwitch --> SkillUsed{"Step 3　Non-super-memory<br/>skill used this turn?"}

    SkillUsed -->|no| NextStep4
    SkillUsed -->|yes, already loaded| NextStep4
    SkillUsed -->|yes, not yet loaded| ReadExpIndex["Read experience/_index.json"]
    ReadExpIndex --> ExpFound{"skill-id found?"}
    ExpFound -->|yes| LoadExp["Load experience/skill-[id].md<br/>mention in reply: experience loaded"]
    ExpFound -->|no| MarkMissing["Add to missing_experience_skills<br/>ask at task end whether to record"]
    LoadExp --> NextStep4
    MarkMissing --> NextStep4

    NextStep4(["Proceed to Step 4: Knowledge Retrieval<br/>(see Diagram 2)"])

